ris\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.942685668325671e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympian has already begun to set milestones as she is both the fourth American woman to compete in a third Olympic games and, at the age of 27, she is the oldest American gymnast to compete at the Olympics in 72 years, while also currently being tied with Shannon Miller for the most Olympic medals earned by a US gymnast.\", \"from\": 3460, \"to\": 3787, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3464, \"end\": 3472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 6.598143733791337e-13, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 3535, \"end\": 3549, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Woman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.788122103239524e-15, \"text\": \"American woman\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Woman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Woman\"}, {\"begin\": 3627, \"end\": 3635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999366691081875, \"rank\": 6.33286847828076e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 3721, \"end\": 3735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shannon_Miller\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5924805812661964e-57, \"text\": \"Shannon Miller\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shannon_Miller\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shannon_Miller\"}, {\"begin\": 3776, \"end\": 3778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.6400826453234331, \"rank\": 0.3205573705441361, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her return to the games comes after she previously competed in both the 2016 Rio games and the 2020 games in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 3789, \"to\": 3904, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3898, \"end\": 3903, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999884726449201, \"rank\": 1.152743656075284e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, she needed to withdraw from most of the 2020 competitions due to a case of the \\\"twisties,\\\" which is a temporary loss of air awareness while performing twisting elements.\", \"from\": 3905, \"to\": 4083, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The brain no longer communicates with the body, they change the move, lose their place,\\\" US women's coach Landi explained in part one of Biles' recent Netflix documentary, titledSimone Biles: Rising.\", \"from\": 4085, \"to\": 4285, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4175, \"end\": 4177, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.6400826453234331, \"rank\": 0.3205573705441361, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 4237, \"end\": 4244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.3537797932463334e-26, \"text\": \"Netflix\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netflix\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Most of the time it's unrelated to gymnastics.\\\"\", \"from\": 4286, \"to\": 4334, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I knew from that one moment,\\\" Biles confessed, reflecting on her Tokyo performance.\", \"from\": 4336, \"to\": 4420, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4402, \"end\": 4407, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999884726449201, \"rank\": 1.152743656075284e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To me it felt silent.\", \"from\": 4421, \"to\": 4443, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I felt like I was in jail in my own brain and body.\\\"\", \"from\": 4444, \"to\": 4496, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This year, the Olympian competed with acalf injuryafter being seen limping on her left ankle.\", \"from\": 4498, \"to\": 4591, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4513, \"end\": 4521, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 6.598143733791337e-13, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although US coach Cecile Landi explained at the time that the injury had only been bothering Biles for a couple of weeks and was considered minor.\", \"from\": 4592, \"to\": 4738, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4601, \"end\": 4603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.6400826453234331, \"rank\": 0.3205573705441361, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Landi added that there were no plans to have her sitting on the sidelines.\", \"from\": 4739, \"to\": 4813, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I can not express it,\\\" Landi said.\", \"from\": 4815, \"to\": 4850, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am really proud of her and what she's been through and what she's showing the world what she's capable of doing.\\\"\", \"from\": 4851, \"to\": 4967, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles posted an all-around total score of 59.566 and the Americans scored a 172.296.\", \"from\": 4969, \"to\": 5053, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All Olympic events are available to watch via cable onNBC, USA Network, or E!The Olympics are also available to stream on Peacock.\", \"from\": 5055, \"to\": 5185, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5114, \"end\": 5125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\", \"score\": 0.9999999999922693, \"rank\": 7.93153555762543e-12, \"text\": \"USA Network\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\"}, {\"begin\": 5177, \"end\": 5184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 0.9999977753720675, \"rank\": 2.1996994865994612e-06, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 5187, \"to\": 5417, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5238, \"end\": 5249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1351430440947154e-20, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Indepen